            "text": "RTB · 2A DAILY INTEL · Thursday, June 25, 2026",
            "spacing": "None"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Large",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "text": "The Court's final week and a new federal front open at once",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "The DOJ has put California on a one-week clock — settle over the “Glock ban” and handgun roster or face suit. Two hard deadlines now sit days apart: June 30 (DOJ–California) and July 1 (Virginia, Colorado).",
            "wrap": true,
            "spacing": "Small"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Small",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "color": "Warning",
            "text": "HOTTEST LEADS",
            "spacing": "Medium"
          },
          {
            "type": "FactSet",
            "facts": [
              {
                "title": "1. DOJ threatens to sue California over the 'Glock ban' & roster",
                "value": "Heat 89 ▲"
              },
              {
                "title": "2. Virginia hardware ban — T-6 to July 1",
                "value": "Heat 87 ▲"
              },
              {
                "title": "3. SCOTUS Wolford v. Lopez — lone pending 2A case",
                "value": "Heat 86 ▲"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Small",
            "weight": "Bolder",
            "color": "Warning",
            "text": "WHAT'S MOVING",
            "spacing": "Medium"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "size": "Small",
            "text": "• DOJ threatens suit over CA Glock ban (AB 1127) & roster — 5pm ET June 30 deadline\n• Judge lets NRA trademark suit vs. its Foundation proceed; control/funds to DC courts\n• Wolford v. Lopez still the lone pending 2A merits case — imminent, not decided\n• Duncan v. Bonta at ~20th relist — term's final conference is this week",
            "wrap": true
